text: Poliaenus volitans is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by John Lawrence LeConte in 1873. It is known from Guatemala and Mexico.BioLib.cz - Poliaenus volitans. Retrieved 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 1873
title: Poliaenus volitans
